query:
UPDATE
                                debian_repository_release
                            SET
                                description = $2,
                                origin = $3,
                                label = $4,
                                version = $5,
                                suite = $6,
                                codename = $7,
                                contents = $8,
                                clearsigned = $9,
                                detached = $10,
                                updated_at = NOW()
                            WHERE
                                id = $1
